{{plinkp|Body tiara}} [[Talisman]] imbued [[tiaras]] require 1 [[Runecraft]] to make, they range from [[air tiara]]s to [[body tiara]]s and each yield 5 times the amount of experience from runecrafting their respective rune. Making one requires a [[tiara]] and a corresponding talisman to use on the respective altar. This method yields the fastest free-to-play Runecraft experience rates, except for stacked up [[runecrafting cores]]. 

Optimal experience rates of up to 57,000 experience per hour can be attained by using a dangerous [[PvP World]], teleporting to [[Barbarian Village]] using a skull sceptre (i), running to the [[Body Altar]], and making the body tiaras. [[Lumbridge Teleport]] for the closest [[bank]] and repeat. This requires 31 [[Magic]], a [[staff of air]], [[law rune]]s, and [[earth rune]]s, as well as enough [[bone fragments]] to recharge the [[skull sceptre (i)]]. [[Energy potions]] will be necessary to keep your run [[energy]] up. It may be more efficient to carry [[air rune]]s instead of using a [[staff of air]] in order to lower your weight by 2.5&nbsp;kg at the added cost of spending air runes to teleport.

If avoiding [[PvP World]]s, the closest teleport to a bank is the [[Falador Teleport]]. 

* Experience needed (1-99): 13,034,431
* [[Tiara]]s needed: 347,585
* [[Body talisman]]s needed: 347,585
* Total Cost: {{Coins|{{GEP|Tiara|347585}}+{{GEP|Body talisman|347585}}}}
* [[Body tiara]]s created: 347,585
* Profit/Loss: {{Coins|{{GEP|Body tiara|347585}} - {{GEP|Tiara|347585}} - {{GEP|Body talisman|347585}}}}
* Number of inventories (12{{X}}12): 28,966

===Levels 1-99 – Earth tiaras===
{{plinkp|Earth tiara}} [[Earth tiara]]s yield up to 27,000 experience per hour. Run to the [[Earth Altar]] and then [[Varrock Teleport]], requiring 25 [[Magic]], you must have [[law rune|law]] and [[fire rune]]s with a [[staff of air]] equipped. [[Energy potions]] will be required to keep your run [[energy]] up.

* Experience needed (1-99): 13,034,431
* [[Tiara]]s needed: 401,060
* [[Earth talisman]]s needed: 401,060
* Total Cost: {{Coins|{{GEP|Tiara|401060}}+{{GEP|Earth talisman|401060}}}}
* [[Earth tiara]]s created: 401,060
* Profit/Loss: {{Coins|{{GEP|Earth tiara|401060}} - {{GEP|Tiara|401060}} - {{GEP|Earth talisman|401060}}}}
* Number of inventories (13{{X}}13): 30,850

===Levels 1-99 – Water tiaras===
