{{plinkp|Water tiara}} [[Water tiara]]s yield up to 25,000 experience per hour. Optimally, run to the [[Water Altar]] and then [[Lumbridge Teleport]], requiring 31 [[Magic]], you must have [[law rune|law]] and [[earth rune]]s with a [[staff of air]] equipped. If done on a [[PvP World]] a [[bank chest]] is next to the teleport, saving about 30 seconds per run. [[Energy potions]] will be required to keep your run [[energy]] up.

If you are not teleporting and do not want to use a PvP world, the closest bank is in [[Draynor Village]].

* Experience needed (1-99): 13,034,431
* [[Tiara]]s needed: 434,333
* [[Water talisman]]s needed: 434,333
* Total Cost: {{Coins|{{GEP|Tiara|434333}}+{{GEP|Water talisman|434333}}}}
* [[Water tiara]]s created: 434,333
* Profit/Loss: {{Coins|{{GEP|Water tiara|434333}} - {{GEP|Tiara|434333}} - {{GEP|Water talisman|434333}}}}
* Number of inventories (12{{X}}12): 33,411

===Air tiaras===
[[Air talisman]]s can be [[drop trick]]ed if you haven't progressed in the [[Rune Mysteries]] [[quest]], explained [[Money making guide/Collecting air talismans|here]]. This is very slow experience and recommended only for [[ironman mode]].

